column15:
Set software clear by hardware.
0: Disable SHA reset.  
1: Enable SHA reset.

Hardware clear after encrypts process finish. 
0: NA. 
1: SHA start, clear by Hardware.

SHA input , 以512bit區塊為一單位,
第一次寫入的為512bit中的[511:480],
第二次寫入的為512bit中的[479:448], 以此類推.

SHA data length[58:32] (unit : 4byte)
不足請直接當4byte計算,
ex: 5byte sha input, SHA_DATALEN = 2

SHA data length[31:0] (unit : 4byte)
不足請直接當4byte計算,
ex: 5byte sha input, SHA_DATALEN = 2

if data bit數 mod 512 小於448  : [512-(bit數 mod512)-64]/32  (不是整數的話無條件進位 )
if data bit數 mod 512 大於等於448  : [512-(bit數 mod512)+448]/32(不是整數的話無條件進位 )

Last Word Valid Byte
0: [31:0] valid
1: [31:24] valid
2: [31:16] valid
3: [31:8] valid

Last Word Valid Byte
0: [31:0] valid
1: [31:24] valid
2: [31:16] valid
3: [31:8] valid

if DATALEN %16==0, add external PKCS to encode
0: EXT PKCS disable
1: EXT PKCS enable

Hardware clear after encrypts process finish. 
0: NA. 
1: AES encrypts start, clear by Hardware.

Encryption complete status. Clear By AES_INT set as 1.
0: Not Complete
1: Complete

Set software clear by hardware.
0: Disable encryption circuit reset.  
1: Enable encryption circuit reset.

Clear AES_E_STA status flag.
Write only. Read always 0.
Software write 1 to clear AES_STA.

AES128 : AES KEY [127:96]
AES256 : AES key[255:224]

AES128 : AES KEY[95:64]
AES256 : AES key[223:192]

AES128 : AES key[63:32]
AES256 : AES key[191:160]

AES128 : AES key[31:0]
AES256 : AES key[159:128]

AES input data, 
第一次寫入的為AES要加密的資料128bit中的[127:96],
第二次寫入的為AES要加密的資料128bit中的[95:64],  以此類推. 不足的部分會自動補上padding bit

AES data length (Unit: 4byte)
不足4byte請直接當4byte算, 
ex: 5byte aes input, AES_DATALEN = 2
bypass sha control when dma enable
bypass aes control when dma enable

1: Enable  DMA reset.
